'''寬吻海豚屬'''（[[學名|學名]]：''Tursiops''）是[[海豚科|海豚科]]下最為人所知及普遍的一類。<ref name=encyc/>[[分子生物學|分子生物學]]研究顯示其下有兩個[[物種|物種]]：[[瓶鼻海豚|瓶鼻海豚]]及[[印太洋瓶鼻海豚|印太洋瓶鼻海豚]]，而非只有一種。牠們棲息在[[溫帶|溫帶]]的海域。

寬吻海豚屬會以10-30條的群落生活，有些數量可以少至1條或達至成千條。牠們主要吃[[魚類|魚類]]。牠們有時會合作捕捉魚群，也有獨自覓食的。牠們主要是靠[[回聲定位|回聲定位]]來尋找獵物。牠們會發出[[聲音|聲音]]及聽其[[回聲|回聲]]來確定身邊物件（包括獵物）的位置及大小。牠們也會利用聲音及身體語言來溝通。

寬吻海豚屬具有高度的[[智慧|智慧]]，包括模仿、使用[[人工語言|人工語言]]、物件分類及自我認知等，這促使牠們與[[人類|人類]]之間的互動。牠們在[[水族箱|水族箱]]非常受歡迎，也有受訓來進行[[水雷|水雷]]及敵方蛙人定位。在一些地區，牠們可以與漁民合作將魚群引到漁網中。

== 分類 ==
傳統上，寬吻海豚屬只有一個[[物種|物種]]，故不能分辨其結構。而[[國際自然保護聯盟|國際自然保護聯盟]]因此在[[IUCN紅色名錄|IUCN紅色名錄]]缺乏數據。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.iucnredlist.org/search/details.php?species=22563|title=''Tursiops truncatus'': Species Information|publisher=IUCN|accessdate=2006-11-03|archive-date=2018-11-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181119173431/https://www.iucnredlist.org/search/details.php?species=22563|dead-url=no}}</ref>分子遺傳學提供了更好的工具來進行研究，並發現共有兩個物種：<ref name="Rice 1998">{{cite book en|author=Rice, Dale W|title=Marine mammals of the world: systematics and distribution (Special Publication)|publisher=Society of Marine Mammalogy|year=1998|id=ISBN 1-891276-03-4}}</ref>

[[File:Tursiops_aduncus.JPG|thumb]]。]]
* [[寬吻海豚|寬吻海豚]]（''T. truncatus''）：分佈在[[熱帶|熱帶]]至[[溫帶|溫帶]]的[[海洋|海洋]]。身體呈灰色，配以藍灰色、褐灰色或近黑色的陰影。吻背至背鰭後一般較為深色；<ref name=princeton>{{cite book en|title=Whales Dolphins and Other Marine Mammals of the World|author=Shirihai, H. and Jarrett, B.|pages=155–161|year=2006|id=ISBN 0-691-12757-3|publisher=Princeton Univ. Press|location=Princeton}}</ref>
* [[印太洋瓶鼻海豚|印太洋瓶鼻海豚]]（''T. aduncus''）：分佈在近[[印度|印度]]、北[[澳洲|澳洲]]、南[[中國|中國]]、[[紅海|紅海]]及[[非洲|非洲]]東岸的海域。背部呈深灰色，[[腹部|腹部]]呈淺灰色或白色，且有灰色斑點。<ref name=princeton/>

以下的有時被認為是寬吻海豚的[[亞種|亞種]]：
* 太平洋寬吻海豚（''T. gillii''或''T. truncatus gillii''）：分佈在[[太平洋|太平洋]]，由[[眼睛|眼睛]]至前額有一道黑線。<ref name=MSW3>{{MSW3 Cetacea|id=14300099}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Catalog of Living Whales|url=http://www.ubio.org/apps/Hershkovitz/index.php?func=s&ID=42&t=s|accessdate=2008-10-01|archive-date=2018-08-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180831211905/http://www.ubio.org/apps/Hershkovitz/index.php?func=s&ID=42&t=s|dead-url=no}}</ref>
* 黑海寬吻海豚（''T. truncatus ponticus''）：分佈在[[黑海|黑海]]。<ref name=MSW3/><ref>{{cite web|title=Convention of International Trade in Endanged Species of Wild Flora and Fauna|url=http://www.cites.org/eng/cop/11/prop/14.pdf|format=PDF|accessdate=2008-10-01|date=April 2000|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081002043753/http://www.cites.org/eng/cop/11/prop/14.pdf|archivedate=2008-10-02}}</ref>

寬吻海豚在西北[[大西洋|大西洋]]有兩個[[生態型|生態型]]：<ref name=ecotype>{{cite web|title=Bottlenose Dolphin (''Tursiops truncatus''): Western North Atlantic Offshore Stock|url=http://www.nmfs.noaa.gov/pr/pdfs/sars/ao2003dobn-wnos.pdf|format=PDF|accessdate=2008-09-30|archive-date=2017-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170516235445/http://www.nmfs.noaa.gov/pr/pdfs/sars/ao2003dobn-wnos.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>即較淺水或近岸的生態型及離岸的生態型。<ref name=ecotype/>牠們的分佈地重疊，但遺傳[[基因|基因]]上各有不同。<ref name=ecotype/>不過，牠們並沒有被描述為不同的物種或亞種。一般而言，牠們具有足夠的群落遺傳變異來描述為獨立的物種。<ref name=princeton/>

一些[[遺傳學|遺傳學]]證據指印太洋瓶鼻海豚屬於[[細吻海豚屬|細吻海豚屬]]，因其外觀較像[[花斑原海豚|花斑原海豚]]而多於寬吻海豚。<ref name="LeDuc 1999">{{cite journal en|author=LeDuc R.G., Perrin W.F. and Dizon A.E.|title=Phylogenetic relationships among the delphinids cetaceans based on full cyctochrome b sequences|journal=Marine Mammal Science|year=1999|volume=15|pages=619–48|doi=10.1111/j.1748-7692.1999.tb00833.x}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal en|title=Phylogenetic Relationships among the Delphinid Cetaceans Based on Full Cytochrome B Sequences|url=http://www3.interscience.wiley.com/journal/119937779/abstract|author=Leduc, R., Perrin, W. & Dizon, E.|date=1998-08-18|journal=Marine Mammal Science|volume=15|issue=3|pages=619–648|doi=10.1111/j.1748-7692.1999.tb00833.x|accessdate=2008-10-05|archive-date=2012-06-04|archive-url=https://archive.today/20120604003637/http://www3.interscience.wiley.com/journal/119937779/abstract}}</ref>

[[File:Baby_wolphin_by_pinhole.jpeg|thumb]]的[[鯨豚|鯨豚]]。]]

=== 混種 ===
寬吻海豚屬與其他[[海豚|海豚]]都有[[混種|混種]]。野生及圈養的情況下，寬吻海豚屬都有與[[灰海豚|灰海豚]]都有混種。<ref name=riss>{{cite book en|title=Guide to Marine Mammals of the World|url=https://archive.org/details/guidetomarinemam00folk|author=Reeves, R.; Stewart, B.; Clapham, P.; Powell, J.|year=2002|pages=[https://archive.org/details/guidetomarinemam00folk/page/422 422]|isbn=0-375-41141-0|publisher=A.A. Knopf|location=New York}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Risso's Dolphin – American Cetacean Society|url=http://www.acsonline.org/factpack/RissosDolphin.htm|accessdate=2008-09-20|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070711025653/http://www.acsonline.org/factpack/RissosDolphin.htm|archivedate=2007-07-11}}</ref>[[鯨豚|鯨豚]]是[[偽虎鯨|偽虎鯨]]與寬吻海豚的混種。鯨豚具生殖能力，現有兩條在[[夏威夷海洋公園|夏威夷海洋公園]]（Sea Life Park），第一條是於1985年出生的雌性鯨豚。鯨豚也有野生的。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.livescience.com/animals/ap_050415_wolphin.html|title=Whale-Dolphin Hybrid Has Baby 'Wholphin'|last=Lee|first=Jaennette|date=2005-04-15|publisher=Associated Press|accessdate=2008-09-20|archive-date=2020-08-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200802052602/https://www.livescience.com/6982-whale-dolphin-hybrid-baby-wholphin.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>圈養的寬吻海豚屬與[[糙齒海豚|糙齒海豚]]有混種。<ref>{{cite web|title=The Mammals of Texas – Rough-toothed Dolphin|url=http://www.nsrl.ttu.edu/tmot1/stenbred.htm|accessdate=2008-09-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080915025738/http://www.nsrl.ttu.edu/tmot1/stenbred.htm|archive-date=2008-09-15|dead-url=yes}}</ref>在[[加利福尼亞州|加利福尼亞州]]的[[海洋世界|海洋世界]]（SeaWorld）出生了寬吻海豚屬及[[海豚屬|海豚屬]]的混種。<ref>{{cite web |title=Robin's Island Database about captive Dolphins and Whales |url=http://www.robins-island.org/dolphins_database.php?filter=Sea_World_California |accessdate=2008-09-20 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090123214019/http://www.robins-island.org/dolphins_database.php?filter=Sea_World_California |archivedate=2009-01-23 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal en|title=Captive-born bottlenose dolphin × common dolphin (''Tursiops truncatus'' × ''Delphinus capensis'') intergeneric hybrids|author=Zornetzer H.R.; Duffield D.A.|journal=Canadian Journal of Zoology|volume=81|issue=10|pages=1755–1762|date=2003-10-01|year=2003|url=http://www.ingentaconnect.com/content/nrc/cjz/2003/00000081/00000010/art00014?crawler=true|publisher=NRC Research Press|doi=10.1139/z03-150|access-date=2010-06-13|archive-date=2016-08-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160827220609/http://www.ingentaconnect.com/content/nrc/cjz/2003/00000081/00000010/art00014?crawler=true|dead-url=no}}</ref>其他的包括與[[花斑原海豚|花斑原海豚]]的混種<ref>{{cite journal en |author=Herzing, D., Moewe, K., & Brunnick, B. |year=2003 |url=http://www.trustedpartner.com/docs/library/000059/Herzing%20Moewe%20Brunnick%20final.pdf |format=PDF |title=Interspecies interactions between Atlantic spotted dolphins, ''Stenella frontalis'' and bottlenose dolphins, ''Tursiops truncatus'', on Great Bahama Bank, Bahamas |journal=Aquatic Mammals |volume=29 |issue=3 |pages=335–341 |accessdate=2008-09-20 |doi=10.1578/01675420360736505 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070614013211/http://www.trustedpartner.com/docs/library/000059/Herzing%20Moewe%20Brunnick%20final.pdf |archivedate=2007-06-14 }}</ref>，其大小會按棲息環境而改變。除了在東[[太平洋|太平洋]]外，在較溫暖及淺水的海豚會較為細小。<ref name=encyc>{{cite book en|title=Encyclopedia of Marine Mammals|url=https://archive.org/details/encyclopediaofma2002unse|author=Wells, R. and Scott, M.|chapter=Bottlenose Dolphins|editor=Perrin, W.; Wursig, B. and Thewissen, J.|pages=[https://archive.org/details/encyclopediaofma2002unse/page/122 122]–7|year=2002|publisher=Academic Press|isbn=0-12-551340-2}}</ref>

== 特徵 ==
寬吻海豚屬呈灰色，頂部近背鰭位置由深灰色至淺灰色，[[腹部|腹部]]呈接近白色。[[反蔭蔽|反蔭蔽]]令牠們不易被看見。成年長2-4米及重150-650公斤。<ref name="acs">{{Cite web |author=American Cetacean Society Fact Sheet |url=http://www.acsonline.org/factpack/btlnose.htm |title=Bottlenose Dolphin |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080725121057/http://www.acsonline.org/factpack/btlnose.htm |archivedate=2008-07-25 |access-date=2010-06-13 }}</ref>雄性平均稍長及較重。在大部份地區，雄性約長2.5米及重200-300公斤。<ref name="princeton"/>

寬吻海豚屬的壽命可以多過40歲。<ref name=audubon/><ref name=protected>{{cite web|title=Office of Protected Resources – Bottlenose Dolphin (Tursiops truncatus)|url=http://www.nmfs.noaa.gov/pr/species/mammals/cetaceans/bottlenosedolphin.htm|accessdate=2008-09-30|archive-date=2017-07-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170725141305/http://www.nmfs.noaa.gov/pr/species/mammals/cetaceans/bottlenosedolphin.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>不過在[[美國|美國]][[佛羅里達州|佛羅里達州]][[薩拉索塔|薩拉索塔]]（Sarasota）的研究卻發現牠們只有平20歲或更少的壽命。<ref>{{cite web|title=Bottlenose Dolphins – Longevity and Causes of Death|url=http://www.seaworld.org/infobooks/Bottlenose/deathdol.html|accessdate=2008-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080914002923/http://www.seaworld.org/infobooks/Bottlenose/deathdol.html|archive-date=2008-09-14|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

== 構造 ==
寬吻海豚屬的上下顎較長。其真正的鼻子是在頭頂上的[[噴氣孔_(生物學)|噴氣孔]]，當噴氣孔打開時，可以清晰看見其[[鼻中隔|鼻中隔]]。

[[File:Bottlenose_Dolphin_KSC04pd0178_head_only.JPG|thumb]]。]]
寬吻海豚屬上下顎每邊各有18-28顆錐狀[[牙齒|牙齒]]。<ref name=audubon>{{cite book en|title=National Audubon Society Guide to Marine Mammals of the World |author=Reeves, R.; Stewart, B.; Clapham, P.; Powell, J.|pages=362–5|year=2002|id=ISBN 0-375-41141-0|publisher=A.A. Knopf|location=New York}}</ref><ref name=marinebio>{{cite web|title=Bottlenose Dolphin ''Tursiops truncatus'' at MarineBio.org|url=http://marinebio.org/species.asp?id=33|accessdate=2008-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080406065404/http://marinebio.org/species.asp?id=33|archive-date=2008-04-06|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

尾巴及背鰭是由高[[密度|密度]]的[[結締組織|結締組織]]組成，並不含有[[骨頭|骨頭]]或[[肌肉|肌肉]]。它們的動力是靠上下擺動尾巴。胸鰭是用來操舵的，內中有與陸上[[哺乳動物|哺乳動物]]相同的骨頭。在[[日本|日本]]的寬吻海豚屬在近尾巴位置有兩條額外的胸鰭，大小如[[人類|人類]]的[[手掌|手掌]]。[[科學家|科學家]]相信這是[[返祖現象|返祖現象]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/15581204/?GT1=8717|title=Dolphin reveals an extra set of 'legs'|accessdate=2007-07-05|archive-date=2012-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121020180846/http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/15581204/?GT1=8717|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

== 生理及感官 ==
在較寒冷的海域，寬吻海豚屬有較多的[[脂肪|脂肪]]及[[血液|血液]]，較為適合潛入深海。一般其體重的18–20%為[[鯨脂|鯨脂]]。<ref name=busch>{{cite web|url=http://www.buschgardens.org/infobooks/Bottlenose/adapaqdol.html|title=Bottlenose Dolphins: Adaptations for an Aquatic Environment|access-date=2010-06-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080517100421/http://www.buschgardens.org/infobooks/Bottlenose/adapaqdol.html|archive-date=2008-05-17|dead-url=yes}}</ref>大部份的研究都只限於北[[大西洋|大西洋]]。<ref name="Hersh 1990">{{cite book en|last=Hersh|first=Sandra L.|coauthors=Deborah A. Duffield|year=1990|chapter=Distinction Between Northwest Atlantic Offshore and Coastal Bottlenose Dolphins Based on Hemoglobin Profile and Morphometry|editor=Stephen Leatherwood and Randall R. Reeves|title=The Bottlenose Dolphin|pages=129–39|location=San Diego|publisher=Academic Press|id=ISBN 0-12-440280-1}}</ref>

=== 回聲定位 ===
寬吻海豚屬是靠[[聲納|聲納]]形式的[[回聲定位|回聲定位]]來幫助覓食。它們會發出[[聲音|聲音]]，並聽取其[[回聲|回聲]]來替物件定位。牠們會在前頭發出喀喇聲的寬帶脈衝群，並利用眼後兩隻細小的耳穴來聆聽回聲，不過大部份的聲波則是經下顎傳入[[內耳|內耳]]。當物件接近時，其回聲漸大，牠們就會調低發出聲音的強度及增加[[頻度|頻度]]。牠們會等待每一次喀喇聲的回聲後才發出另一次。[[科學家|科學家]]也有就訊號強度、聲譜性質等進行研究。<ref name="Au">{{cite book en|last=Au|first=Whitlow|year=1993|title=The Sonar of Dolphins|url=https://archive.org/details/sonarofdolphins0000auwh|location=New York|publisher=Springer-Verlag}}</ref>牠們甚至可以從中獲得物件形狀的資訊。<ref name="Pack 1995">{{cite journal en|author=Pack AA, Herman LM|title=Sensory integration in the bottlenosed dolphin: immediate recognition of complex shapes across the senses of echolocation and vision|journal=The Journal of the Acoustical Society of America|volume=98|issue=2 Pt 1|pages=722–33|pmid=7642811|doi=10.1121/1.413566|date=August 1995}}</ref>

=== 視覺 ===
寬吻海豚屬的[[視覺|視覺]]非常敏銳。[[眼睛|眼睛]]位於[[頭部|頭部]]兩側，並有[[絨氈層|絨氈層]]可以在暗光下幫助視覺。牠們的[[瞳孔|瞳孔]]呈馬蹄狀及有雙縫，令牠們在水中及[[空氣|空氣]]中也可以有很好的視覺。<ref name="Herman 1975">{{cite journal en|last=Herman|first=L. M.|coauthors=Peacock, M. F., Yunker, M. P. & Madsen, C.|year=1975|title=Bottlenosed dolphin: Double-slit pupil yields equivalent aerial and underwater diurnal acuity|journal=Science|volume=139|pages=650–2|doi=10.1126/science.1162351|pmid=1162351|issue=4203}}</ref>當在水中時，其[[眼球|眼球]]內的[[晶體|晶體]]用來聚焦光線；但當在空氣中時，充足的光線會令瞳孔收縮，形成精確度高的影象。

=== 嗅覺 ===
寬吻海豚屬的[[嗅覺|嗅覺]]很差<ref name=characteristics>{{cite web|title=Dolphin Characteristics|url=http://www.wiu.edu/users/emp102/DolphinWeb/dolphin_char.htm|accessdate=2008-08-31|archive-date=2021-06-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210621144236/http://www.wiu.edu/users/emp102/DolphinWeb/dolphin_char.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，這是由於其鼻子（[[噴氣孔_(生物學)|噴氣孔]]）在水中是緊閉有關。牠們的[[腦部|腦部]]沒有[[嗅神經|嗅神經]]或[[嗅葉|嗅葉]]。<ref name=characteristics/>牠們可以分辨鹹味、甜味、苦味及酸味。<ref name=characteristics/>一些圈養的寬吻海豚屬對某些食物有特別偏好，但並不清楚是否與嗅覺有關。<ref name=characteristics/>

=== 溝通 ===
寬吻海豚屬會以吱吱聲、吹哨聲及身體語言來溝通。身體語言的例子包括跳出水面、咬顎、拍尾及頭撞。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nationalgeographic.com/kids/creature_feature/0108/dolphins2.html |title=Bottlenose Dolphins: Animal information, pictures, map |publisher=National Geographic |accessdate=2006-11-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20061023104744/http://www.nationalgeographic.com/kids/creature_feature/0108/dolphins2.html |archivedate=2006-10-23 }}</ref>[[聲音|聲音]]及動作可以在群落中記錄其他成員的位置，也可以通報危險及食物。由於沒有[[聲帶|聲帶]]，牠們是利用近[[噴氣孔_(生物學)|噴氣孔]]的6個氣囊來發聲。每一隻寬吻海豚屬都有獨特的發聲聲頻。<ref name="Janik 1998">{{cite journal en|author=Janik VM, Slater PJB|title=Context-specific use suggests that bottlenose dolphin signature whistles are cohesion calls|journal=Animal Behaviour|volume=56|issue=4|pages=829–38|pmid=9790693|doi=10.1006/anbe.1998.0881|date=October 1998}}</ref>雖然[[約翰‧立利|約翰‧立利]]（John C. Lilly）於1950年代提倡沒有海豚語言，但現已分辨了其他30種聲音。也有學者展示了兩隻寬吻海豚屬的[[人工語言|人工語言]]詞彙。<ref name="Herman 1984">{{cite journal en|author=Herman LM, Richards DG, Wolz JP|title=Comprehension of sentences by bottlenosed dolphins|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_cognition_1984-03_16_2/page/129|journal=Cognition|volume=16|issue=2|pages=129–219|pmid=6540652|doi=10.1016/0010-0277(84)90003-9|date=March 1984}}</ref>

